# CSS, BEM, and responsive layout

- Use external stylesheets only; no inline styles for presentation.
- Prefer class selectors; use BEM: `.block`, `.block__element`, `.block--modifier`.
- Define theme tokens in `:root` (CSS variables); use `rem`/`em` for typography and spacing where practical.
- Layout with Flexbox and/or Grid; mobile-first `@media` (min-width).
- Visible `:focus-visible` styles; avoid `!important` unless overriding third-party with no alternative.
- Touch targets at least ~44×44px for primary interactive controls in navigation and forms.

```css
/* Avoid */
#header { color: red !important; }

/* Prefer */
.site-header {
  color: var(--color-text);
}
```
